<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Harness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Harness,</orth> 1) the furniture of a draught horse: <bibl n="shak. per 5.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 44.</bibl><lb />2) armour: <cit><quote>he doth fill fields with h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.101" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 101</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>doff thy h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 3, 31</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.5.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 5, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 8, 15</bibl>.
